  "time_ut": 1656518588,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0da2\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dbb \u0db8\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0db8\u0dda \u0dbb\u0ddd\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dc4 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dab\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc5 \u0dad\u0dd2\u0db6\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"The country has world-class hospitals and adequate human resources.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lanka Medical Association says that the country has international standard hospitals and adequate human resources to make it a tourist destination for medical treatment.",
        "The association said that every 10 minutes there is an accident in the country which kills 8 people a day and kills more than 3000 people every year and many of them become permanently inactive.",
        "The Sri Lanka Medical Association (SLMA) said that although various agencies have taken various measures for road safety, all of them should work together to formulate policy decisions based on accurate data and set up a Presidential Task Force to make recommendations for this purpose.",
        "The association spoke on a number of issues, including the need for essential medicines, medical equipment, laboratory chemicals, and the prevention of food shortages and possible nutritional deficiencies in society.",
        "He was speaking at a meeting with President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa at the Presidential Palace in Colombo.",
        "A delegation led by Prof. Samath Dharmawardena, President of the Sri Lanka Medical Association participated in the discussion.",
        "Secretary to the President Gamini Senarath, Chief of Staff to the President Anura Dissanayake, IGP CD Wickramaratne, Deputy Chairman of the Medical Council Dr. Susantha Perera and others were present at the occasion."
      ],
